OL,3,CTom Parker's widow reveals she is
OL,4,Cpregnant with 'rainbow baby' after
OL,5,Cstillbirth
OL,7,FThe widow of The Wanted singer Tom
OL,8,FParker has announced that she's
OL,9,Fpregnant with a 'rainbow baby',
OL,10,Ffollowing the stillbirth of her with
OL,11,Fbaby with her new partner.
OL,13,FKelsey Parker revealed the news with a
OL,14,Fpicture of her baby scan, posted on
OL,15,FInstagram.
OL,17,FIn the post, she said: "A year ago
OL,18,Fnext month, we lost our beautiful baby
OL,19,Fboy, Phoenix.
OL,26,@yD@XOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
