PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780236666
OL,3,CTom Parker's widow reveals she is
OL,4,Cpregnant with 'rainbow baby' after
OL,5,Cstillbirth
OL,7,F"And somehow, through all the
OL,8,Fheartbreak, it feels like Tom and
OL,9,FPhoenix have sent us another little
OL,10,Fgift from heaven our little rainbow
OL,11,Fbaby."
OL,13,FTom Parker, who was from Bolton, died
OL,14,Fin 2022 at the age of 33 after being
OL,15,Fdiagnosed with an inoperable brain
OL,16,Ftumour. The pair married in 2018, and
OL,17,Flater had two children.
OL,19,FPresenter of Good Morning Britain
OL,20,FSusanna Reid was among the celebrities
OL,21,Fcongratulating Kelsey on the birth.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@FO]
