PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780236666
OL,3,CTom Parker's widow reveals she is
OL,4,Cpregnant with 'rainbow baby' after
OL,5,Cstillbirth
OL,7,F"Obviously, straight away we called
OL,8,Fthe ambulance. They took nine minutes
OL,9,Fto come, and just when they arrived...
OL,10,Fthe only way I can describe it, it was
OL,11,Flike I was in a film, and this wasn't
OL,12,Freal, and it wasn't happening to me."
OL,14,FShe said they took Phoenix and called
OL,15,Fthe police, who told her that her home
OL,16,Fwas a "crime scene".
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@eO]xD@GOUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
