FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780236666
OL,3,CTom Parker's widow reveals she is
OL,4,Cpregnant with 'rainbow baby' after
OL,5,Cstillbirth
OL,7,FParker, who is campaigning for better
OL,8,Fcare for those who have lost a baby,
OL,9,Fsaid the situation got worse as they
OL,10,Ftook Phoenix away and she was told to
OL,11,Fattend the hospital maternity unit
OL,12,Fwhere she had to wait to be seen
OL,13,Fsurrounded by mothers and their
OL,14,Fnewborn babies.
OL,16,FPolice have since apologised to
OL,17,FParker, and she was told the
OL,18,Fparamedics who attended her house had
OL,19,Fnever seen a stillborn baby before.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
