PN,39207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1780236666
OL,3,CTom Parker's widow reveals she is
OL,4,Cpregnant with 'rainbow baby' after
OL,5,Cstillbirth
OL,7,FA Metropolitan Police spokesperson
OL,8,Fsaid: "We understand this was a deeply
OL,9,Ftraumatic experience for Kelsey and
OL,10,FWill and our thoughts remain with them
OL,11,Fas they continue to grieve the loss of
OL,12,Ftheir son.
OL,14,F"We acknowledge that referring to the
OL,15,Faddress as a crime scene was
OL,16,Finappropriate, and that the family
OL,17,Fcould and should have been treated in
OL,18,Fa more sensitive way.
OL,26,@pD@GOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
